DISCLAIMER FOR PORTFOLIO/EDUCATIONAL PROJECT

This project is designed for educational and portfolio demonstration purposes.
While production-quality code practices have been followed, this software has
not undergone a professional security audit and should not be used with real
funds or in production environments without proper security review and testing.

Use at your own risk.

For production use:
- Conduct a professional security audit
- Implement full Merkle proof verification
- Add challenge period mechanism
- Use hardware wallets for key management
- Implement comprehensive monitoring and alerting
- Follow all applicable regulations and compliance requirements

The author(s) and contributor(s) are not responsible for any loss of funds or
damages resulting from the use of this software.
